Name: VER\_REP\_CR\_FD
Description: Failure code for start actions when they unsuccessfully attempt to create a new report from the OutFactory

Name: VER\_OUTLOADER\_FD
Description: Failure code for start actions when the Load operation in the OutLoader has failed

Name: VER\_SID\_IN\_USE
Description: Failure code for start action of commands (3,1) and (3,2) when attempt to create a new report with a SID which is already in use

Name: VER\_FULL\_RDL
Description: Failure code for start action of commands (3,1) and (3,2) when they attempt to create a new report at a time when the RDL is already full

Name: VER\_RDL\_CONSTr
Description: Failure code for start action of commands (3,1) and (3,2) when their report configuration data violate an RDL constraint of table \ref{tab:repDefDataStruct}
VerFailData: The identifier of the violated constraint

Name: VER\_DUPL\_DI
Description: Failure code for start action of commands (3,1) and (3,2) when they carry the same data item identifier twice

Name: VER\_ILL\_SID
Description: Failure code for start action of a service 3 command when an illegal SID is encountered

Name: VER\_ENBABLED\_SID
Description: Failure code for start action of commands (3,3) and (3,4) when a SID which is enabled is encountered

Name: VER\_SID\_START\_FD
Description: Failure code for start action of multi-instruction service 3 commands when all the SIDs in the command are found to be invalid

Name: VER\_FACT\_PRGR\_FD
Description: Failure code for progress action of multi-instruction service 3 command when the attempt to retrieve a report from the OutFactory fails
VerFailData: The SID for which the retrieval from the OutFactory was attempted

Name: VER\_ILL\_EID
Description: Failure code for start action of a service 5 command when an illegal EID is encountered

Name: VER\_EID\_START\_FD
Description: Failure code for start action of multi-instruction service 5 commands when all the EIDs in the command are found to be invalid
